The paper discusses the role of big data analytics in the design of data communication networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also touches upon security and privacy concerns (cs.CR), data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.SI) in the context of network design. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, and cs.SI.
